i'm putting this out there because it needs saying and many of you out there are experiencing the same thing. big problem some of the dickhead dealers are making the weed seen dirty, its getting treated like the powder seen, eg: scamming, underweight, all looks good but has no punch, overpaying, over exagerating. this shit is reserved for the the harder scene. i think most of you get the general idea. dope is the last bastion in the drug seen where honesty is still its greatest selling tool. this is a fact, users are not your every day scatter brain juice head. most are respectable citizens. this goes without say. the clown dealers i speak of would have been out of business on their first few sales anywhere else. i've come back to the home country after living overseas for few years and i can't believe the price of dope and all the bullshit hype around it. this is like watching an infant grow up and mature. i'll explain what i mean. in australia i have tried all the so called, juicy fruit, gorilla, cheese. all falling within the 3 categories indica, sativa or hybrid, just to keep it simple. i will agree some of it is strong smelling but that's all it is, it doesn't pack the punch like the real juicy fruit and black widow and the all the other top shelf gear. it also lacks the staying power, try the same thing in europe and now usa, its different, for those of you that have tried it, you know what i'm talking about. for those that haven't well i can tell you, the stuff here doesn't compete. those that tell you it does, either haven't been over there or they've been told by jo blow, you know those types they know everything but been nowhere. i can't believe how loosely the medical' term is used, most of the good gear described qualifies as medical grade overseas here the word medical is the trigger to bump up the price, or they stick a name on it, this gear here is considered just average shit overseas. these clowns that claim to be the savior and messiah to the sick by supplying them medical grade for there illness and crank up the price are fucking maggots not all but there's a lot. they are just taking advantage of the disadvantaged. this is wrong, i'm not having a go at aussie weed, it is what it is and getting better it's the wank factor i'm talking about. more and more people are waking up to this and seeing whats real. i'm having a go at the bullshit hype people use, its a joke but hey i guess we are a small population and don't know any better, we're evolving. then i've read some adds where it appears their doing you a big bloody favor these people are legends in their own lunchtime. there are some good ones dealers hard to find, mine is great,no hype, no bullshitting around, backs up what they sell always and is honest. i'm in and out as fast as i want to be. no 007 sneaking around bullshit. i'm happy with that and would let you know if and when the gear is not so great and priced accordingly hasn't happened yet, for me this means a lot and i greatly appreciate it. its all up front and wouldn't dare bullshit you knowing once you smoke up you wont be happy, that's how it works everywhere in the world. i respect their privacy and good attitude i'm just paying homeage. hi there, remember conversation small sausages for breakfast small sausages for breakfast see you soon. most of all they dont treat anybody like a fool and is smarter than most out there peddling what they consider premium quality that turns out to be shit, i say this to all you poor bastards being told its the supreme or it's kouda or any other fucking bullshit just beware, look around try small first and see, don't get stuck with shit just cause it smells great or they tell you it's the greatest and overpaying. these dealers are not here for you but here for their pocket only. there are too many so called experts that claim or appear to be fully conversant, they just spend too much time reading on the net and lack experience. they overcharge something like $130 $140 a quarter thats just greed and the smoke is average for what you pay. even $100, still too high for a descent smoke be it indica, sativa or hybrid. its not worth the money here. don't get fooled by a strong smell or led to believe strong smell strong smoke. no not always the case. these people consider a good customer a buyer of large quantities. that's yesterdays world, one of the great benefits of hydro apart from availability and strength is having variety anytime, comes down to quality and quality alone. the majority of their business will come from the smaller buyers that's the trend. the smart guys already know this. just look at california whats going on. medical cannabis will be in full swing soon, the supply side is ramping up before we start seeing more dispensaries opening up and australia is set to become the largest grower in the southern hemisphere. it will rake in billions for aus. there are some predominate aussie billionaires one group i know of is ex mining buying up thousands of hectares for this purpose. i believe in west aust, gina rhinehardt, richest women in aus has bought in with a large tobacco co and the wa gov has a stake in it. the affect on the black market as we know it and not far away is the price drop all round, dealers you're going to get a huge shake up. the market will be flooded even though it becomes medically legal and controlled, adversely the black market will boom, it will become the buyers market, you'll be scratching for turnover if you don't sharpen your pencil. people, bide your time and remember the greedy ones charging $130 $140 and more prices as well as the hike on halfs and o's will be history. yes i know the price drop starts from the top of the chain, some of us are not totally fucking stupid especially when you are paying same price for a pound whether its good average or great, and feel you can flog it for more because its called bla bla bla or it smells fantastic some of you dealers, not all, are the biggest joke overseas and now some of the usa uni fraternities have compiled lists informing travelers about aussie and nz dealers the good, the <h> bad </h> and the ugly. i'm sure its already begun here dob in a rip off or something like that the perception in europe is that dope here is way overpriced for average stuff. many dealers preying on the public s vulnerability. what about this money gram thing going on here, you deposit money and wait for a call to confirm. i mean wtf, and its supposed keep things secure. secure for them, its not like you're peddling nuclear arms for fuck sake this would put you in a whole lot of trouble overseas. a dealer using this method would raise alarm bells and signal that they have a whole lot of quantity on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they for them, its not like you're peddling nuclear arms for fuck sake this would put you in a whole lot of trouble overseas. a dealer using this method would raise alarm bells and signal that they have a whole lot of quantity on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need him her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next time i come across one of these shit heads that do this your getting exposed on here, clean your fucking act up. if you cant treat people or customers properly and think its cool letting them wait or selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 drop offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you stick the thing and you dont have to do all this other shit. make the late thing a rarity not the norm. this to me is fairly easy not hard to look after them properly. happy days ahead people power rules.

i'm putting this out there because it needs saying and many of you out there are experiencing the same thing. big problem some of the dickhead dealers are making the weed seen dirty, its getting treated like the powder seen, eg: scamming, underweight, all looks good but has no punch, overpaying, over exagerating. this shit is reserved for the the harder scene. i think most of you get the general idea. dope is the last bastion in the drug seen where honesty is still its greatest selling tool. this is a fact, users are not your every day scatter brain juice head. most are respectable citizens. this goes without say. the clown dealers i speak of would have been out of business on their first few sales anywhere else. i've come back to the home country after living overseas for few years and i can't believe the price of dope and all the bullshit hype around it. this is like watching an infant grow up and mature. i'll explain what i mean. in australia i have tried all the so called, juicy fruit, gorilla, cheese. all falling within the 3 categories indica, sativa or hybrid, just to keep it simple. i will agree some of it is strong smelling but that's all it is, it doesn't pack the punch like the real juicy fruit and black widow and the all the other top shelf gear. it also lacks the staying power, try the same thing in europe and now usa, its different, for those of you that have tried it, you know what i'm talking about. for those that haven't well i can tell you, the stuff here doesn't compete. those that tell you it does, either haven't been over there or they've been told by jo blow, you know those types they know everything but been nowhere. i can't believe how loosely the medical' term is used, most of the good gear described qualifies as medical grade overseas here the word medical is the trigger to <h> bump up </h> the price, or they stick a name on it, this gear here is considered just average shit overseas. these clowns that claim to be the savior and messiah to the sick by supplying them medical grade for there illness and crank up the price are fucking maggots not all but there's a lot. they are just taking advantage of the disadvantaged. this is wrong, i'm not having a go at aussie weed, it is what it is and getting better it's the wank factor i'm talking about. more and more people are waking up to this and seeing whats real. i'm having a go at the bullshit hype people use, its a joke but hey i guess we are a small population and don't know any better, we're evolving. then i've read some adds where it appears their doing you a big bloody favor these people are legends in their own lunchtime. there are some good ones dealers hard to find, mine is great,no hype, no bullshitting around, backs up what they sell always and is honest. i'm in and out as fast as i want to be. no 007 sneaking around bullshit. i'm happy with that and would let you know if and when the gear is not so great and priced accordingly hasn't happened yet, for me this means a lot and i greatly appreciate it. its all up front and wouldn't dare bullshit you knowing once you smoke up you wont be happy, that's how it works everywhere in the world. i respect their privacy and good attitude i'm just paying homeage. hi there, remember conversation small sausages for breakfast small sausages for breakfast see you soon. most of all they dont treat anybody like a fool and is smarter than most out there peddling what they consider premium quality that turns out to be shit, i say this to all you poor bastards being told its the supreme or it's kouda or any other fucking bullshit just beware, look around try small first and see, don't get stuck with shit just cause it smells great or they tell you it's the greatest and overpaying. these dealers are not here for you but here for their pocket only. there are too many so called experts that claim or appear to be fully conversant, they just spend too much time reading on the net and lack experience. they overcharge something like $130 $140 a quarter thats just greed and the smoke is average for what you pay. even $100, still too high for a descent smoke be it indica, sativa or hybrid. its not worth the money here. don't get fooled by a strong smell or led to believe strong smell strong smoke. no not always the case. these people consider a good customer a buyer of large quantities. that's yesterdays world, one of the great benefits of hydro apart from availability and strength is having variety anytime, comes down to quality and quality alone. the majority of their business will come from the smaller buyers that's the trend. the smart guys already know this. just look at california whats going on. medical cannabis will be in full swing soon, the supply side is ramping up before we start seeing more dispensaries opening up and australia is set to become the largest grower in the southern hemisphere. it will rake in billions for aus. there are some predominate aussie billionaires one group i know of is ex mining buying up thousands of hectares for this purpose. i believe in west aust, gina rhinehardt, richest women in aus has bought in with a large tobacco co and the wa gov has a stake in it. the affect on the black market as we know it and not far away is the price drop all round, dealers you're going to get a huge shake up. the market will be flooded even though it becomes medically legal and controlled, adversely the black market will boom, it will become the buyers market, you'll be scratching for turnover if you don't sharpen your pencil. people, bide your time and remember the greedy ones charging $130 $140 and more prices as well as the hike on halfs and o's will be history. yes i know the price drop starts from the top of the chain, some of us are not totally fucking stupid especially when you are paying same price for a pound whether its good average or great, and feel you can flog it for more because its called bla bla bla or it smells fantastic some of you dealers, not all, are the biggest joke overseas and now some of the usa uni fraternities have compiled lists informing travelers about aussie and nz dealers the good, the bad and the ugly. i'm sure its already begun here dob in a rip off or something like that the perception in europe is that dope here is way overpriced for average stuff. many dealers preying on the public s vulnerability. what about this money gram thing going on here, you deposit money and wait for a call to confirm. i mean wtf, and its supposed keep things secure. secure for them, its not like you're peddling nuclear arms for fuck sake this would put you in a whole lot of trouble overseas. a dealer using this method would raise alarm bells and signal that they have a whole lot of quantity on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need him her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next time i come across one of these shit heads that do this your getting exposed on here, clean your fucking act up. if you cant treat people or customers properly and think its cool letting them wait or selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 drop offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you stick the thing and you dont have to do all this other shit. make the late thing a rarity not the norm. this to me is fairly easy not hard to look after them properly. happy days ahead that they have a whole lot of quantity on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the <h> dope </h> scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the <h> dope </h> scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up <h> dope </h> prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need him her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next time i come across one of these shit heads that do this your getting exposed on here, clean your fucking act up. if you cant treat people or customers properly and think its cool letting them wait or selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 drop offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you stick the thing and you dont have to do all this other shit. make the late thing a rarity not the norm. this to me is fairly easy not hard to look after them properly. happy days ahead people power rules.

i'm putting this out there because it needs saying and many of you out there are experiencing the same thing. big problem some of the dickhead dealers are making the weed seen dirty, its getting treated like the powder seen, eg: scamming, underweight, all looks good but has no punch, overpaying, over exagerating. this shit is reserved for the the harder scene. i think most of you get the general idea. dope is the last bastion in the drug seen where honesty is still its greatest selling tool. this is a fact, users are not your every day scatter brain juice head. most are respectable citizens. this goes without say. the clown dealers i speak of would have been out of business on their first few sales anywhere else. i've come back to the home country after living overseas for few years and i can't believe the price of dope and all the bullshit hype around it. this is like watching an infant grow up and mature. i'll explain what i mean. in australia i have tried all the so called, juicy fruit, gorilla, cheese. all falling within the 3 categories indica, sativa or hybrid, just to keep it simple. i will agree some of it is strong smelling but that's all it is, it doesn't pack the punch like the real juicy fruit and black widow and the all the other top shelf gear. it also lacks the staying power, try the same thing in europe and now usa, its different, for those of you that have tried it, you know what i'm talking about. for those that haven't well i can tell you, the stuff here doesn't compete. those that tell you it does, either haven't been over there or they've been told by jo blow, you know those types they know everything but been nowhere. i can't believe how loosely the medical' term is used, most of the good gear described qualifies as medical grade overseas here the word medical is the trigger to bump up the price, or they stick a name on it, this gear here is considered just average shit overseas. these clowns that claim to be the savior and messiah to the sick by supplying them medical grade for there illness and crank up the price are fucking maggots not all but there's a lot. they are just taking advantage of the disadvantaged. this is wrong, i'm not having a go at aussie weed, it is what it is and getting better it's the wank factor i'm talking about. more and more people are waking up to this and seeing whats real. i'm having a go at the bullshit hype people use, its a joke but hey i guess we are a small population and don't know any better, we're evolving. then i've read some adds where it appears their doing you a big bloody favor these people are legends in their own lunchtime. there are some good ones dealers hard to find, mine is great,no hype, no bullshitting around, backs up what they sell always and is honest. i'm in and out as fast as i want to be. no 007 sneaking around bullshit. i'm happy with that and would let you know if and when the gear is not so great and priced accordingly hasn't happened yet, for me this means a lot and i greatly appreciate it. its all up front and wouldn't dare bullshit you knowing once you smoke up you wont be happy, that's how it works everywhere in the world. i respect their privacy and good attitude i'm just paying homeage. hi there, remember conversation small sausages for breakfast small sausages for breakfast see you soon. most of all they dont treat anybody like a fool and is smarter than most out there peddling what they consider premium quality that turns out to be shit, i say this to all you poor bastards being told its the supreme or it's kouda or any other fucking bullshit just beware, look around try small first and see, don't get stuck with shit just cause it smells great or they tell you it's the greatest and overpaying. these dealers are not here for you but here for their pocket only. there are too many so called experts that claim or appear to be fully conversant, they just spend too much time reading on the net and lack experience. they overcharge something like $130 $140 a quarter thats just greed and the smoke is average for what you pay. even $100, still too high for a descent smoke be it indica, sativa or hybrid. its not worth the money here. don't get fooled by a strong smell or led to believe strong smell strong smoke. no not always the case. these people consider a good customer a buyer of large quantities. that's yesterdays world, one of the great benefits of hydro apart from availability and strength is having variety anytime, comes down to quality and quality alone. the majority of their business will come from the smaller buyers that's the trend. the smart guys already know this. just look at california whats going on. medical cannabis will be in full swing soon, the supply side is ramping up before we start seeing more dispensaries opening up and australia is set to become the largest grower in the southern hemisphere. it will rake in billions for aus. there are some predominate aussie billionaires one group i know of is ex mining buying up thousands of hectares for this purpose. i believe in west aust, gina rhinehardt, richest women in aus has bought in with a large tobacco co and the wa gov has a stake in it. the affect on the black market as we know it and not far away is the price <h> drop </h> all round, dealers you're going to get a huge shake up. the market will be flooded even though it becomes medically legal and controlled, adversely the black market will boom, it will become the buyers market, you'll be scratching for turnover if you don't sharpen your pencil. people, bide your time and remember the greedy ones charging $130 $140 and more prices as well as the hike on halfs and o's will be history. yes i know the price <h> drop </h> starts from the top of the chain, some of us are not totally fucking stupid especially when you are paying same price for a pound whether its good average or great, and feel you can flog it for more because its called bla bla bla or it smells fantastic some of you dealers, not all, are the biggest joke overseas and now some of the usa uni fraternities have compiled lists informing travelers about aussie and nz dealers the good, the bad and the ugly. i'm sure its already begun here dob in a rip off or something like that the perception in europe is that dope here is way overpriced for average stuff. many dealers preying on the public s vulnerability. what about this money gram thing going on here, you deposit money and wait for a call to confirm. i mean wtf, and its supposed keep things secure. secure for them, its not like you're peddling nuclear arms for fuck sake this would put you in a whole lot of trouble overseas. a dealer using this method would raise alarm bells and signal that they have a whole lot of quantity on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need him her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next time i come across one of these shit heads that do this your getting exposed on here, clean your fucking act up. if you cant treat people or customers properly and think its cool letting them wait or selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 <h> drop </h> offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you stick the thing and you dont have to do all this other shit. make the late thing a rarity not the norm. this to me is fairly easy not hard to look after them properly. happy days ahead people power rules.

on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need him her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next time i come across one of these shit heads that do this your getting exposed on here, clean your fucking act up. if you cant treat people or customers properly and think its cool letting them wait or selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 drop offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you stick the thing and you dont have to do all this other shit. make the late thing a rarity not the norm. this to me is fairly easy not hard to look after them properly. happy days ahead people power rules.

i'm putting this out there because it needs saying and many of you out there are experiencing the same thing. big problem some of the dickhead dealers are making the weed seen dirty, its getting treated like the powder seen, eg: scamming, underweight, all looks good but has no punch, overpaying, over exagerating. this shit is reserved for the the harder scene. i think most of you get the general idea. dope is the last bastion in the drug seen where honesty is still its greatest selling tool. this is a fact, users are not your every day scatter brain juice head. most are respectable citizens. this goes without say. the clown dealers i speak of would have been out of business on their first few sales anywhere else. i've come back to the home country after living overseas for few years and i can't believe the price of dope and all the bullshit hype around it. this is like watching an infant grow up and mature. i'll explain what i mean. in australia i have tried all the so called, juicy fruit, gorilla, cheese. all falling within the 3 categories indica, sativa or hybrid, just to keep it simple. i will agree some of it is strong smelling but that's all it is, it doesn't pack the punch like the real juicy fruit and black widow and the all the other top shelf gear. it also lacks the staying power, try the same thing in europe and now usa, its different, for those of you that have tried it, you know what i'm talking about. for those that haven't well i can tell you, the stuff here doesn't compete. those that tell you it does, either haven't been over there or they've been told by jo blow, you know those types they know everything but been nowhere. i can't believe how loosely the medical' term is used, most of the good gear described qualifies as medical grade overseas here the word medical is the trigger to bump up the price, or they stick a name on it, this gear here is considered just average shit overseas. these clowns that claim to be the savior and messiah to the sick by supplying them medical grade for there illness and crank up the price are fucking maggots not all but there's a lot. they are just taking advantage of the disadvantaged. this is wrong, i'm not having a go at aussie weed, it is what it is and getting better it's the wank factor i'm talking about. more and more people are waking up to this and seeing whats real. i'm having a go at the bullshit hype people use, its a joke but hey i guess we are a small population and don't know any better, we're evolving. then i've read some adds where it appears their doing you a big bloody favor these people are legends in their own lunchtime. there are some good ones dealers hard to find, mine is great,no hype, no bullshitting around, backs up what they sell always and is honest. i'm in and out as fast as i want to be. no 007 sneaking around bullshit. i'm happy with that and would let you know if and when the gear is not so great and priced accordingly hasn't happened yet, for me this means a lot and i greatly appreciate it. its all up front and wouldn't dare bullshit you knowing once you smoke up you wont be happy, that's how it works everywhere in the world. i respect their privacy and good attitude i'm just paying homeage. hi there, remember conversation small sausages for breakfast small sausages for breakfast see you soon. most of all they dont treat anybody like a fool and is smarter than most out there peddling what they consider premium quality that turns out to be shit, i say this to all you poor bastards being told its the supreme or it's kouda or any other fucking bullshit just beware, look around try small first and see, don't get stuck with shit just cause it smells great or they tell you it's the greatest and overpaying. these dealers are not here for you but here for their pocket only. there are too many so called experts that claim or appear to be fully conversant, they just spend too much time reading on the net and lack experience. they overcharge something like $130 $140 a quarter thats just greed and the smoke is average for what you pay. even $100, still too high for a descent smoke be it indica, sativa or hybrid. its not worth the money here. don't get fooled by a strong smell or led to believe strong smell strong smoke. no not always the case. these people consider a good customer a buyer of large quantities. that's yesterdays world, one of the great benefits of hydro apart from availability and strength is having variety anytime, comes down to quality and quality alone. the majority of their business will come from the smaller buyers that's the trend. the smart guys already know this. just look at california whats going on. medical cannabis will be in full swing soon, the supply side is ramping up before we start seeing more dispensaries opening up and australia is set to become the largest grower in the southern hemisphere. it will rake in billions for aus. there are some predominate aussie billionaires one group i know of is ex mining buying up thousands of hectares for this purpose. i believe in west aust, gina rhinehardt, richest women in aus has bought in with a large tobacco co and the wa gov has a stake in it. the affect on the black market as we know it and not far away is the price drop all round, dealers you're going to get a huge shake up. the market will be flooded even though it becomes medically legal and controlled, adversely the black market will boom, it will become the buyers market, you'll be scratching for turnover if you don't sharpen your pencil. people, bide your time and remember the greedy ones charging $130 $140 and more prices as well as the hike on halfs and o's will be history. yes i know the price drop starts from the top of the chain, some of us are not totally fucking stupid especially when you are paying same price for a pound whether its good average or great, and feel you can flog it for more because its called bla bla bla or it smells fantastic some of you dealers, not all, are the biggest joke overseas and now some of the usa uni fraternities have compiled lists informing travelers about aussie and nz dealers the good, the bad and the ugly. i'm sure its already begun here dob in a rip off or something like that the perception in europe is that dope here is way overpriced for average stuff. many dealers preying on the public s vulnerability. what about this money gram thing going on here, you deposit money and wait for a call to confirm. i mean wtf, and its supposed keep things secure. secure for them, its not like you're peddling nuclear arms for fuck sake this would put you in a whole lot of trouble overseas. a dealer using this method would raise alarm bells and signal that they have a whole lot of quantity on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need <h> him </h> her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 drop offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and <h> jack </h> up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need him her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next time i come across one of these shit heads that do this your getting exposed on here, clean your fucking act up. if you cant treat people or customers properly and think its cool letting them wait or selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 drop offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you stick the thing and you dont have to do all this other shit. make the late thing a rarity not the norm. this to me is fairly easy not hard to look after them properly. happy days ahead people power rules.

i'm putting this out there because it needs saying and many of you out there are experiencing the same thing. big problem some of the dickhead dealers are making the weed seen dirty, its getting treated like the powder seen, eg: scamming, underweight, all looks good but has no punch, overpaying, over exagerating. this shit is reserved for the the harder scene. i think most of you get the general idea. dope is the last bastion in the drug seen where honesty is still its greatest selling tool. this is a fact, users are not your every day scatter brain <h> juice </h> head. most are respectable citizens. this goes without say. the clown dealers i speak of would have been out of business on their first few sales anywhere else. i've come back to the home country after living overseas for few years and i can't believe the price of dope and all the bullshit hype around it. this is like watching an infant grow up and mature. i'll explain what i mean. in australia i have tried all the so called, juicy fruit, gorilla, cheese. all falling within the 3 categories indica, sativa or hybrid, just to keep it simple. i will agree some of it is strong smelling but that's all it is, it doesn't pack the punch like the real juicy fruit and black widow and the all the other top shelf gear. it also lacks the staying power, try the same thing in europe and now usa, its different, for those of you that have tried it, you know what i'm talking about. for those that haven't well i can tell you, the stuff here doesn't compete. those that tell you it does, either haven't been over there or they've been told by jo blow, you know those types they know everything but been nowhere. i can't believe how loosely the medical' term is used, most of the good gear described qualifies as medical grade overseas here the word medical is the trigger to bump up the price, or they stick a name on it, this gear here is considered just average shit overseas. these clowns that claim to be the savior and messiah to the sick by supplying them medical grade for there illness and crank up the price are fucking maggots not all but there's a lot. they are just taking advantage of the disadvantaged. this is wrong, i'm not having a go at aussie weed, it is what it is and getting better it's the wank factor i'm talking about. more and more people are waking up to this and seeing whats real. i'm having a go at the bullshit hype people use, its a joke but hey i guess we are a small population and don't know any better, we're evolving. then i've read some adds where it appears their doing you a big bloody favor these people are legends in their own lunchtime. there are some good ones dealers hard to find, mine is great,no hype, no bullshitting around, backs up what they sell always and is honest. i'm in and out as fast as i want to be. no 007 sneaking around bullshit. i'm happy with that and would let you know if and when the gear is not so great and priced accordingly hasn't happened yet, for me this means a lot and i greatly appreciate it. its all up front and wouldn't dare bullshit you knowing once you smoke up you wont be happy, that's how it works everywhere in the world. i respect their privacy and good attitude i'm just paying homeage. hi there, remember conversation small sausages for breakfast small sausages for breakfast see you soon. most of all they dont treat anybody like a fool and is smarter than most out there peddling what they consider premium quality that turns out to be shit, i say this to all you poor bastards being told its the supreme or it's kouda or any other fucking bullshit just beware, look around try small first and see, don't get stuck with shit just cause it smells great or they tell you it's the greatest and overpaying. these dealers are not here for you but here for their pocket only. there are too many so called experts that claim or appear to be fully conversant, they just spend too much time reading on the net and lack experience. they overcharge something like $130 $140 a quarter thats just greed and the smoke is average for what you pay. even $100, still too high for a descent smoke be it indica, sativa or hybrid. its not worth the money here. don't get fooled by a strong smell or led to believe strong smell strong smoke. no not always the case. these people consider a good customer a buyer of large quantities. that's yesterdays world, one of the great benefits of hydro apart from availability and strength is having variety anytime, comes down to quality and quality alone. the majority of their business will come from the smaller buyers that's the trend. the smart guys already know this. just look at california whats going on. medical cannabis will be in full swing soon, the supply side is ramping up before we start seeing more dispensaries opening up and australia is set to become the largest grower in the southern hemisphere. it will rake in billions for aus. there are some predominate aussie billionaires one group i know of is ex mining buying up thousands of hectares for this purpose. i believe in west aust, gina rhinehardt, richest women in aus has bought in with a large tobacco co and the wa gov has a stake in it. the affect on the black market as we know it and not far away is the price drop all round, dealers you're going to get a huge shake up. the market will be flooded even though it becomes medically legal and controlled, adversely the black market will boom, it will become the buyers market, you'll be scratching for turnover if you don't sharpen your pencil. people, bide your time and remember the greedy ones charging $130 $140 and more prices as well as the hike on halfs and o's will be history. yes i know the price drop starts from the top of the chain, some of us are not totally fucking stupid especially when you are paying same price for a pound whether its good average or great, and feel you can flog it for more because its called bla bla bla or it smells fantastic some of you dealers, not all, are the biggest joke overseas and now some of the usa uni fraternities have compiled lists informing travelers about aussie and nz dealers the good, the bad and the ugly. i'm sure its already begun here dob in a rip off or something like that the perception in europe is that dope here is way overpriced for average stuff. many dealers preying on the public s vulnerability. what about this money gram thing going on here, you deposit money and wait for a call to confirm. i mean wtf, and its supposed keep things secure. secure for them, its not like you're peddling nuclear arms for fuck sake this would put you in a whole lot of trouble overseas. a dealer using this method would raise alarm bells and signal that they have a whole lot of quantity on them or their vehicle. it has the adverse effect. regardless of this id bullshit, fake id's is also big business. the mentality that a person providing id and parting with money to a machine, wouldn't dare rob them! right moron, would it be delusional to think this method makes you bait foolproof little fish catches the big fish, isn't that how it goes. you remember these dealers who are just pushing their profit as they are going to be the same ones fighting for your business and they will try hard to sweeten the sale and realise the high value of the customer big or small you will never find some disrespectful fuck telling you to go somewhere else if you complained or anything. the people will dictate how much they want to pay and not the dealer. if you don't believe me just ask a smoker that's traveled and look at the trend in other countries. these dealers are only short term operators. it will be everywhere more readily available, the fancy name bullshit wont apply to shit, it will be something like similar or same family or traces of or a type of or wet you get the idea and the expectation will lift. but people will wake up when the real thing is here. they will pay a little more but where for example if its called black widow it will be the same one they smoke in spain or prague or amsterdam just to mention some. it will be the real thing. try and stooge people and see who controls your business then. more and more people will grow there own and they'll get wise and think before they call it the fancy name. competition sorts everything out even the government tobacco companies everybody even drug dealers its a commodity like all other things we consume, like coffee, tea. supermarkets are getting the shake up everywhere all of a sudden organic is available in most of them. only a few years ago you would have to look hard to find somthing like this with reasonable prices its changing. overseas they're everywhere and good prices. this attitude of over charging in our great country has its fangs even in the dope scene. get ready people the tide is turning, i understand everybody has to make money and profit that's a given but these dealers overcharging have to realize that those people that they dealt with and took advantage of on their way up, will be the same people on their way down. the dope scene in other countries where its considered soft or tolerated. dealers wouldn't dare try and jack up dope prices like here its considered an insult, price fluctuation does happen but its hardly noticeable, its the harder drugs, they are whats expensive. i hope some of you get what i'm saying here as i speak for the underdog and i'm aware some of the audience will disagree and rant and rave.guess who? its all good by me if it gets a reaction. everywhere else in the world! in the event you were sold shit and you complain they will rectify it immediately and i mean go out of their way as it puts their business in jeopardy. what is noticeable all over most good real dealers in the world never act big they may think it and never crap on enlightening you with their knowledge to reinforce the sales. the product,doesn't need talking up and for them to patronize you. wouldn't overcharge, this would spell liquidation for them. one last thing to all these wankers, discrete means discrete why bring an other level of bullshit to the table that says i'm fucking paranoid as because i'm carrying around other seedy shit, thats fine but dont put your paranoia bullshit on me the customer. this is your fucken problem not ours the buyers and already you are waving a red flag. has anyone encounter this shit or leave you waiting around or 30 min is 2 hours or rings 10 min after the arranged time. dont deal with these flogs, they cant manage their time means everything else is crappy. they are supposed to make it smooth as possible not have this attitude of high status as everybody need him her. the customer is just the money source. it's a business like all others legal or illegal the mechanics is the same. and the movement of goods is largely due to its customer. suppliers there are many and will be more. next time i come across one of these shit heads that do this your getting exposed on here, clean your fucking act up. if you cant treat people or customers properly and think its cool letting them wait or selling shit. you will be a looser in any business you touch even legitimate. you will never get anywhere in any business or venture if you cant manage your time and i dont give a fuck if you have a 20 drop offs, firstly i dont want to know what goes on in your business and dont be a dickhead exposing your activity to me to justify your downfalls. not my fucking problem if you said a time you stick the thing and you dont have to do all this other shit. make the late thing a rarity not the norm. this to me is fairly easy not hard to look after them properly. happy days ahead
